\par\keepn
\par \plain \keepn\f0\fs20 
\deflang2057\pard\plain\f3\fs24\cf0 The Sales screen is displayed by clicking 'Tables|Sales' and shows the last thousand sales for a particular till. If the zero till is selected, then all sales are shown. Further information can be obtained by selecting a particular sale and then clicking Details.\plain\f5\fs20\cf0 \
 \
 \
