{\*\bkmkstart _topicpageref_Salestaxes}{\*\bkmkend _topicpageref_Salestaxes}\par \pard\plain \s2\keepn\tx1200\b\f6\fs32 18.15.\tab Sales taxes
\par\keepn
\par \plain \keepn\f0\fs20 
\deflang2057\pard\plain\f3\fs24\cf0 The sales tax modify screen is straightforward. The tax rates are set up initially for the UK, so that users abroad may need to change these. A separate tax rate for rental (Video) is included even though this is the same as the standard rate in Britain, as this allows for a separation of the takings, from normal sales.\plain\f5\fs20\cf0 \
 \
 \
 \plain\f3\fs24\cf0 
\par\pard
