\par\keepn
{\v{\xe {stock}}}{\v{\xe {SKU}}}{\v{\xe {stockID}}}{\v{\xe {yield}}}{\v{\xe {return on investment}}}\par \plain \keepn\f0\fs20 
\deflang2057\pard\plain\f3\fs24\cf0 The Stock modify screen shows the stock record associated with products.
