\deflang2057\pard\plain\f3\fs24\cf0 Selecting 'Tables|Taxes causes the Taxes screen to be displayed showing the description, rate, symbol and code are displayed for each entry. Initially, the data is set up for UK VAT rates, but these can be modified by selecting and then clicking the Details button. The symbol is the indication given on receipts and is a single character. Code is the ID in the table.
